OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny residual
OL,6,Fshowery rain across Kent this evening
OL,7,Fsoon clearing to leave a dry night
OL,8,Fwith clear periods, although high
OL,9,Flevel cloud increasing later. Winds
OL,10,Fdecreasing with some patchy ground
OL,11,Ffrost possible by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FChilly start, then bright
OL,14,Fspells through the morning but cloud
OL,15,Fthickens through the afternoon,
OL,16,Fperhaps bringing a little patchy light
OL,17,Frain eastwards. Breezier by the
OL,18,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
