OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand strong winds Saturday morning,
OL,7,Fclearing to sunny spells and scattered
OL,8,Fshowers. Sunday, breezy with sunshine
OL,9,Fand showers. Monday, fewer showers and
OL,10,Flighter winds. Temperatures mostly
OL,11,Faround average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
